This would be done like this:

```zsh
local last
zstyle -s ':prompt:shrink_path' last last

case "$last" in
  (false|no|off|0) lastfull=0 ;;
  (true|yes|on|1) lastfull=1 ;;
  (""|*[^0-9]*) lastfull=0 ;;
  (*) lastfull=$last ;;
esac
```

